	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have used Calm as well as the lower Lull often. I think the problem is that you nuke the other mob. After a mob looks less aggresive I or the puller walk up and whack the other, most often the one I calmed stays put. I am not to your level yet so I am not sure about how those mobs will react but give it a try.<br><br>Kiresretaw<br>Cleric of Tunare 24th season<br>Zebuxuruk<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
